## Data Propagation

The **Deliveries Order Type** flows through the posting chain:

```
Purchase Header
  └── Deliveries Order Type
        │
        ├──▶ Item Journal Line
        │    └── Deliveries Order Type
        │
        └──▶ Item Ledger Entry
             └── Deliveries Order Type
```

This enables reporting and analysis on item ledger entries by delivery type.